property_details: Luxurious Living and Dining: With breathtaking views as the backdrop, spacious indoor and outdoor living and dining areas have been thoughtfully designed for entertaining with porcelain slab, wood or marble floors. Floor-to-ceiling glass leads to expansive balconies and irresistible views of the bay and vibrant downtown.

Feature Rich Kitchens: Exceptional, purpose-driven kitchens are contemporary gathering spaces where flawless design and culinary connoisseurs intertwine. Sleek Italian cabinetry, signature finishes, and a comprehensive suite of built-in Subzero® and Wolf® premium appliances further delight your culinary imagination.

Owners Suites: Enjoy convenience and ease offered through a hand-crafted master closet and private midnight bar featuring understated designs that are equally functional as they are elegant. Your owner's suite is your quiet escape featuring magnificent floor-to-ceiling glass that leads to your private, expansive balcony with stunning vistas of Sarasota.

Owners Bath: The owner's bath is designed as a graceful retreat curated with top-tier features and finishes. The extravagant space features imported Italian cabinetry, custom countertops and WaterWorks® fixtures. Frameless shower doors, exquisite marble, and a luxurious soaking tub create a serene spa-like atmosphere.

Expansive Terraces: Sarasota offers year-round enjoyment of outdoor living. Step onto your glass-railed terraces and treat yourself to an unobstructed panorama of the Bay and Downtown skyline. These generous terraces offer summer kitchens and relaxing opportunities to entertain and enjoy beautiful sunsets over the water.

Smart Home Technology: One Park's smart home technology gives you control of your home's lighting, climate, and entertainment from a single, easy-to-use app. Whether you’re creating the perfect atmosphere for a dinner party or turning on lights and your favorite music before getting home at night, smart home technology makes it easy to have everything exactly the way you like it.

Penthouse Collection: The highest residences in Sarasota, the One Park penthouse collection soars above the 53-acre park, giving panoramic views of the Gulf. These four exquisite, private residences feature grand entrances, expansive living spaces, and state-of-the-art finishes. Each penthouse has a massive private rooftop terrace featuring a private plunge pool, summer kitchen and multiple entertainment areas.

The Views: Exquisitely designed and reaching into the skyline, One Park offers magnificent views of downtown Sarasota and its beautiful bayfront sunsets. Nestled on a 53-acre park, lush green landscapes unfold below.
amenity_details: Amenity Deck: One Park’s amenity deck has a full range of signature offerings including a One Park wellness spa, resort-style pool, state-of-the-art fitness studio, dog run, and a well-appointed guest suite for your family and friends. Entertain and dine in the private Wine Room or Club Room with catering kitchen. One Park is fully staffed to assist your every desire including a concierge, valet, and more.

Resort style pool: The swimming pools at One Park are the heart and center of the action. It’s the place where guests can socialize, relax, see and be seen. These pools represent idyllic escapes from the hectic pace of daily life. Featuring hot and cold plunge pool jacuzzis, a juice bar, stay-cool spa deck and sweeping lounge areas which are perfect for entertaining family and friends or simply enjoying the peace and quiet at day's end.

Wellness Spa: Whether your goal is to stay fit or simply wind down and relax, our One Park Wellness Spa offers a wide range of revitalizing amenities, including a Hammam Spa, private His and Hers lockers, saunas, and steam rooms.

Fitness Club: Whether you're just starting a fitness program or following your current one, the state-of-the-art Fitness Club at One Park is the perfect way to find your strength. The latest exercise equipment and cardio machines are sure to present the challenge, while the Pilates, Yoga and Cycling rooms help you set the tone. Get ready to find your motivation here in the exceptional bayside setting of the Fitness Club at One Park.

Social Rooms: When it comes to an environment where a sense of community is encouraged, One Park takes your social network to a whole new level. Enjoy the private theater for movie nights or entertain in the club room, wine room, lounge area, or golf simulator. There's something for every family member and guest.

Concierge Service: From the valet staff who welcome you to the knowledgeable concierge staff who assist with booking prized dining reservations and activities, the One Park team is always at your service. Services include, 24-hour security with access-controlled entry points, Package delivery service, Lockable storage, Dog walking service, On-site property management, Secured Wi-Fi in all amenity areas
The Quay Yacht Basin: Adjacent to One Park, the Quay Yacht Basin provides direct boating access to Sarasota Bay, the Gulf of Mexico, and beyond.
developer_details: Founded in 1991 by Kevin Maloney, Property Markets Group ("PMG") is a national real estate development firm with offices in Miami and Manhattan, specializing in exceptional new construction commercial and residential projects.
The company has direct hands-on experience in the acquisition, renovation, financing, operation, and marketing of commercial and residential real estate.
A development firm of national scope, PMG has spearheaded over 150 real estate transactions, including over 80 residential buildings in Manhattan during its 25-year history.

PMG has distinguished itself over the last decade for its focus on premier luxury residential properties in the most coveted locations. Known for meticulous design and construction, the energetic team is relentlessly dedicated to making bold improvements to skylines and streetscapes.
architect_details: Hoyt Architects is renowned for their immersive design process. It creates a deeper understanding of each project by studying design parameters ranging from mass, scale, topography, circulation, sun orientation and lighting to materials, texture and finishes.
For more than 40 years, Hoyt Architects has designed hundreds of projects around the U.S.
builder_details: Founded in 1997, Atlanta-based Juneau Construction Company rapidly grew from a two-employee, wife-and-husband business to a more than $400 million company with more than 190 employees and offices in Atlanta, Miami and Tampa.

Juneau is a Top 50 Southeast regional contractor and among the premiere builders of higher education facilities and multifamily buildings throughout Georgia, Florida, Tennessee, South Carolina, and Alabama.
